---
title: Steak and Crispy Potato Salad with Tomatoes, Green Beans and Shallot Pan Sauce
description: Our Spanish-inspired potato salad boasts crispy potatoes and fresh green beans for a side salad like you’ve never had before. The only thing that could meet the challenge of pairing with this masterpiece is a juicy pan-seared steak, cooked to perfection.
